fitdists for fitdistrplus fluazinam Data

Source: R/data.R
fluazinam_dists.Rd

A fitdists object for Species Sensitivity Data for Fluazinam.

fluazinam_dists

Format

An object of class fitdistscens (inherits from fitdists) of length 3.

See also

fluazinam
